org.engineeringnotebook.glassfishmonitor.instance
Class InstanceListStatusObserver

java.lang.Object
  org.engineeringnotebook.glassfishmonitor.instance.InstanceListStatusObserver
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable, Observer
public class InstanceListStatusObserver
extends Object
implements Observer, Runnable

This class implements the observer portion of the (GoF) Observer pattern and listens for updates from the InstanceListMonitor (subject). The listener will wait a specific amount of time for an update from the monitor. If it doesn't receive an update, the thread will terminate.

Author:
Jeffrey Coble http://engineeringnotebook.org
